                        FontCache Guide

Guide Version 1.11                       FontCache Version 1.9

____________________________________________________________________________


Prologue:       I thought the folks at H&P and Amiga Inc. would have taken
the chance to add this to the 3.5 (V44) edition of the diskfont.library, I
would have even released the sources for free. Unfortunately, they still
left me with a diskfont.library which scans three minutes for fonts.

____________________________________________________________________________


This release contains a new version of the "FixFonts" program. Never ever
try to run this, nor the original "FixFonts", on an "AFS" partition. The AFS
implementation of ExAll() is buggy and might either crash or hang. This is
not a "FixFonts" problem! Either re-install the FFS, or any other *working*
filing system.

